                requester_contact, provider_pubkey, offering_id,

                duration_hours, original_duration_hours, request_memo,
                created_at_ns, status, payment_method, stripe_payment_intent_id, stripe_customer_id, payment_status
            ) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)
